thread.title_full: Nengun Performance について 投稿者 subydug.

author: subydug.
title: subydug.
text: I ordered the BH5 hood scoop for my 05 Turbo Baja and Nengun was very prompt on the delivery to the US. They kept me informed of the status of my my parts, and when it was going out for shipping. I received it in a very well packaged box, and it came complete with everything I needed for the install. The product fit in perfectly and replaces the OEM one with no issues at all. I will be using them again in the future.
